<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西确认了没人在看她以后，悄悄跑到学校教学楼的后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在一瞬间，她变身成为了火箭女孩儿！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是时候去找出潘校长失踪的原因了。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她飞向空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！是火箭女孩儿！”玛拉叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她这是去哪里呢？”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们知道罗西去哪里了吗？”他问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西在警察总局落了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她找到了史密斯侦探。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他正坐在桌子前，盯着他的电脑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您这是在看电视节目吗？”罗西笑道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您不应该在破案吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73083</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探皱了皱眉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没有在看电视节目。我在看一段交通录像。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长给我打电话了。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他告诉我，潘校长失踪了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她没有失踪。”史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她离开了小镇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>事实上，美罗城小学所有的老师都离开了小镇。你看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看了看交通录像。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>录像里面有很多汽车和公交车经过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿！那是潘校长！”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114477</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“接着看。”史密斯侦探说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114478</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来是艾普卡特老师。紧接着是格林老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西学校的老师们一个接着一个，开着车经过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126565</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是西大街。”史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“通往美罗城外的山上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所有的老师开着车去山上了？”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我猜是的。”史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这说不通啊。为什么所有的老师会在工作日去山上呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150873</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们现在应该在教书！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150874</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西又看了一遍录像。这次她发现了什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的老师们胸前都别着一模一样的星星胸针！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而且所有的胸针都在发着光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我见过这些胸针！”罗西叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“思维普斯老师，那个代理校长，他把胸针都发给了学生们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你确定吗？”史密斯侦探问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那太值得怀疑了。我们需要……火箭女孩儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西一瞬间就到达了美罗城小学。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她冲进大门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205421</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“思维普斯老师在哪里？”罗西喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>走廊是空着的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人在吗？”罗西叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有人回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西冲进了教室里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有人在。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>校长室里面也是空着的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西很快意识到，整个学校都是空着的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232478</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家都去了哪里呢？”她思索着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要用我的超级听力了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几秒之后，她听到了什么声音，并且是非常奇怪的声音！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>